After liaising with several of them, I decided to go with this one, as they seemed the most promising. I was particularly impressed with Anne, their online WhatsApp contact. He not only fixed the problem in record time, but also took the time to explain what had caused the clog in the first place, and gave me helpful tips to prevent it from happening again. He was friendly, polite, and ensured everything was running perfectly before he left.

The entire experience, from liaising with Anne to Casmir’s quick and expert work, was seamless. I couldn’t have asked for better service. If you’re looking for a reliable plumber who delivers fast results without compromising on quality, I highly recommend this team. You’ll be in good hands!

Their prices are very reasonable as well. I would certainly call them up for future jobs.

text.text: I highly highly recommend Jerry from Plumbing Hub. I called him early in the morning to explain we had a problematic drain blockage (very messy!).  He came by with all the necessary equipment, did a thorough analysis of the pipe network and immediately went to rectify the issue. The blockage was cleared and Jerry went the extra mile to clear the mess that the blockage had caused in the toilet, we were extremely grateful. Jerry took the time to explain to us the underlying problems to ensure we knew how to prevent this in the future. This is absolutely 5 star service, reliable, honest, reasonable rates, and highly professional. I'm calling him again should I need some help!
